title: redsn0w-mac_0.3.zip
description:
redsn0w v0.3 (beta)

This is a beta release of redsn0w for Mac OS X. 
Currently this version is command line only. The functionality will be delivered with a GUI soon and also incorporated into our other easy to use applications.

redsn0w is a Mac OS X based jailbreak tool for the iPod touch 2G. For full details about the iPhone DevTeam releases and other background information visit the iphone DevTeam blog. http://blog.iphone-dev.org
